Whimsical Characters.description: Flat, minimalistic cartoon style with bold, clean black outlines and a whimsical, friendly mood.
Kawaii, minimal, and feminine with playful repetitive motifs, pastel colors, and clean outlines.
Whimsical, hand-drawn cartoon style with bold linework, playful imperfections, and vibrant, childlike watercolor accents.
Playful, hand-drawn cartoon style with bold outlines, childlike features, imperfect scribbles, and whimsical, artsy charm.
Modern, playful, and minimalist illustration with bold, contrasting colors and whimsical, hand-drawn elements.

Artistic.description: Modern boho line-art with minimalist, expressive outlines and subtle vintage tones in an organic, densely layered floral composition.
Playful, crayon-style folk art with a whimsical, hand-drawn appearance.

Jungle & Animal.description: Modern naturalistic style with realistic wildlife and detailed botanical illustration in a seamless, vibrant composition.

Minimalist and Doodles.description: Minimalist, hand-drawn cartoon doodles in a monochrome, Scandinavian-inspired style with playful, childlike lines and sparse accent colors.
Clean, modern cartoon line art with selective pops of bright color against minimalist black outlines.
Playful, messy, and joyful childlike crayon doodle style with wobbly, uneven lines and spontaneous, imperfect details.

Folk and Ethnic.description: The style is a rustic, hand-drawn, folk-inspired pattern based on traditional Indian Warli art, featuring minimal, geometric figures and symbolic storytelling in earthy tones.

A realistic, painterly style blending intricate architectural illustration with lush, immersive tropical foliage, rendered in warm, earthy tones and rich gradients for a serene, vintage postcard feel.
